The evidence with the title 'Measles Data And Statistics ' says Feb 16, 2018  ... Great progress has been made towards measles elimination  ... Number of lives saved by measles vaccine globally . Source: mmwr: Oct 27, 2017 / vol. 66 / No. 42 . 3  ... The last measles death in the United States occurred in 2015 .  ... Diarrhea is reported in less than one out of 10 people with measles . 
